overview:
Sticviews are personalized prints that go anywhere and come off clean. You can stylize your world with colorful creations that will not fade indoors or out; decorate anything with easy to apply adhesive prints that stic without getting stuck; are designed your way with your images or images in the gallery and made to any size and shape.

People came to the founders from all over with crazy ideas for sticviews, so much so that they couldn’t keep up with all the suggested ideas! So they decide to create http://sticviews.com, a place where you can create your own, design your own, personalize it, size it, and choose from unlimited combinations of shapes and sizes, colors, patterns, images, and text. Sticviews is an online community where people share their designs with others. The website has a “my sticviews” user page where you can save your designs, share with friends, and even the home page is full of great ideas from the user community, because you are the creative ones, sticviews is just the platform.

Sticviews uncovered many magical materials in our research that extend beyond window applications. So they now offer materials that stic to walls, windows, doors, cars, appliances, electronics, laptops, cell phones, desks, and even fabric! All the materials have the same great properties: vivid full color photo quality imagery, good for indoor or outdoor use, low tac adhesive, residue free removal, and repositionable so you can reuse them over and over again. The best part is they are so affordable, much more so than other forms of art or decorations, and the amazing thing is each sticview is especially custom made just for you!

The best part is that sticviews are for everyone. Kids, teens, college students, professionals, home, business, vehicles, moms, dads, all have countless ways to “renew your view” and show their “personal expressions of style” with sticviews.
